            Try It YourselfThis editor is fully interactive. Try these:Type / to open the slash command menu and insert any block typeSelect text to see the floating toolbar with formatting optionsHover on the left of any block to drag it or open block actionsUse keyboard shortcuts like Cmd+B for bold, Cmd+I for italic, Cmd+Z to undoCheck out the other examples in the sidebar to see Yoopta Editor in different use cases: email builder, Slack-like chat, collaborative editing, and more.
